<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.1.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2020-10-29T16:15:56+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, over 16 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">River at Dawn・夜明けの川</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201029/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="River at Dawn・夜明けの川" /><published>2020-10-29T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-29T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/river-at-dawn</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201029/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Boats on the shallow Oi River wait patiently in the early morning, while the leaves start to change colors.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    大堰川の船は早朝に待ちます。 紅葉が始まります。
      
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Boats" /><category term="Dawn" /><summary type="html">Boats on the shallow Oi River wait patiently in the early morning, while the leaves start to change colors.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R00018.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Yellow Station・黄色い駅</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201027/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Yellow Station・黄色い駅" /><published>2020-10-27T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-27T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/yellow-station</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201027/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Bright yellow ceiling at &lt;a href=&quot;/190525/&quot;&gt;Kyoto Station&lt;/a&gt;, one of many colorful details in architect &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hiroshi_Hara_(architect)&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Hiroshi Hara&lt;/a&gt;’s design.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    &lt;a href=&quot;/190525/&quot;&gt;京都駅&lt;/a&gt;の明るい黄色の天井。 これは、&lt;a href=&quot;https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8E%9F%E5%BA%83%E5%8F%B8&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;原広司&lt;/a&gt;の建築デザインに、おける多くのカラフルなディテールの1つです。
      
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Trains" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">Bright yellow ceiling at Kyoto Station, one of many colorful details in architect Hiroshi Hara’s design.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R00006.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Arashiyma Sunrise・嵐山の日の出</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201025/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Arashiyma Sunrise・嵐山の日の出" /><published>2020-10-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sunrise</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201025/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    I got up early to catch the sun rising over Kyoto’s eastern mountains, reflecting in the Katsura River.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
   東山に昇る朝陽が桂川に映るのを見るために早起きしました。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">I got up early to catch the sun rising over Kyoto’s eastern mountains, reflecting in the Katsura River.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09978-HDR.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Miyama Autumn Leaves・美山の紅葉</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201024/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Miyama Autumn Leaves・美山の紅葉" /><published>2020-10-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/miyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201024/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Autumn leaves starting to turn at &lt;a href=&quot;https://miyamanavi.com/en/sightseeing/kayabuki-no-sato&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Miyama Kayabuki no Sato&lt;/a&gt;, a village of traditional thatched roof homes deep in the mountains, north of Kyoto.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
   京都北部の山奥にある&lt;a href=&quot;https://miyamanavi.com/sightseeing/kayabuki-no-sato&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;美山かやぶきの里&lt;/a&gt;で紅葉が始まります。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Views" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html">Autumn leaves starting to turn at Miyama Kayabuki no Sato, a village of traditional thatched roof homes deep in the mountains, north of Kyoto.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09907.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Above Kitasaga・北嵯峨からの眺め</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201015/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Above Kitasaga・北嵯峨からの眺め" /><published>2020-10-15T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-15T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kitasaga</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201015/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Looking southeast from Kitasaga, the northwest corner of Kyoto.
&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    In the distance, upper right, is Kyoto Tower; the buildings get smaller as you get closer to Kitasaga, with farmland in between the two ponds:  Hirosawa Ike on the left, and Osawa Ike bottom right - adjacent to Daikaku-ji Temple. 
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
北嵯峨から京都の眺めです。
&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
遠くに見えるのは京都タワーです。北嵯峨に近づくにつれ、建物は小さくなります。左が広沢池、右下が大覚寺に隣接する大沢池、池の間に農地があります。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Views" /><category term="Ponds" /><summary type="html">Looking southeast from Kitasaga, the northwest corner of Kyoto. In the distance, upper right, is Kyoto Tower; the buildings get smaller as you get closer to Kitasaga, with farmland in between the two ponds: Hirosawa Ike on the left, and Osawa Ike bottom right - adjacent to Daikaku-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09615.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sogenchi Garden・曹源池庭園</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201013/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sogenchi Garden・曹源池庭園" /><published>2020-10-13T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-13T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sosenchi</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201013/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    The leaves are starting to turn at Tenryu-ji Temple.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
天龍寺では葉が色づき始めています。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><summary type="html">The leaves are starting to turn at Tenryu-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09579.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Togetsu Bridge Panorama・渡月橋のパノラマ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201012/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Togetsu Bridge Panorama・渡月橋のパノラマ" /><published>2020-10-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/togetsu-pano</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201012/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    A wide angle panorama on a warm, sunny day in Arashiyama.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
嵐山の暖かく晴れた日の広角パノラマ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Panoramas" /><summary type="html">A wide angle panorama on a warm, sunny day in Arashiyama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09507-Pano.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sunlight &amp;amp; Shadow・日光と影</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201011/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunlight &amp;amp; Shadow・日光と影" /><published>2020-10-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sun-and-shadow</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201011/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Late afternoon sun casts shadows on a platform at Kyoto Station.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
   京都駅のプラットホームに、午後遅くの太陽が影を落とします。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Trains" /><category term="Black and White" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">Late afternoon sun casts shadows on a platform at Kyoto Station.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09497.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Katsura Sunrise・桂川の日の出</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201007/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Katsura Sunrise・桂川の日の出" /><published>2020-10-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/katsura-sunrise</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201007/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Pampas grass at the edge of the Katsura River in Arashiyama this morning.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    今朝の嵐山の桂川のほとりで見たススキ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">Pampas grass at the edge of the Katsura River in Arashiyama this morning.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09397.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Zuiho-in・瑞峯院</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201006/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Zuiho-in・瑞峯院" /><published>2020-10-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/zuiho-in</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201006/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    The main hall and “Dokuza-tei” dry landscape garden at Zuiho-in, one of the subtemples at &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daitoku-ji&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Daitoku-ji&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
   

    大徳寺内の瑞峯院の本堂と、枯山水の庭園「独坐庭」。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Gardens" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">The main hall and “Dokuza-tei” dry landscape garden at Zuiho-in, one of the subtemples at Daitoku-ji.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R09349-HDR.jpg" /></entry></feed>